-- Swatch Says 2012 Sales May Rise as Much as 10%, Reuters Reports
-- B y   D e r m o t   D o h e r t y
-- 2012-01-10T13:31:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-10/swatch-says-2012-sales-may-rise-as-much-as-10-reuters-reports.html
Swatch Group AG (UHR)  said revenue may
increase 5 percent to 10 percent in 2012,  Reuters  reported,
citing Chief Executive Officer Nick Hayek.  Profit will also rise as the watchmaker expands its
distribution network and adds products, Reuters cited Hayek as
saying in an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dermot Doherty in Geneva  at 
